of his own story yesterday

51:27.367 --> 51:29.934
as what many industry insiders
called a ratings stunt

51:30.000 --> 51:31.333
backfired.

51:31.400 --> 51:32.967
Convicted murderer
Cyril O'Reily

51:33.033 --> 51:35.400
