causing the veteran reporter

51:35.467 --> 51:37.033
to suffer
a severe concussion,

51:37.100 --> 51:39.266
four broken ribs,
and a punctured lung.

51:39.333 --> 51:42.200
He remains at Benchley Memorial
in critical condition.

51:42.266 --> 51:44.667
Despite the objections
of Eldridge's producer,

51:44.734 --> 51:46.433
