the network has decided

51:46.500 --> 51:48.200
not to air
what was intended to be

51:48.266 --> 51:50.367
a three-part series
on life inside

51:50.433 --> 51:52.633
Oswald's maximum
security prison.

51:52.700 --> 51:55.166
